===============================================================================
BUDGET INSIGHT ERA (2012-2023)
===============================================================================

During 2012-2023, Budget Insight significantly contributed to woob development,
particularly in banking and financial modules. Their contributions represent
a major portion of the project development. Key contributors included:

Baptiste Delpey <bdelpey@budget-insight.com>
        * Lead banking API architect and CapBankTransfer creator;
        * PSD2 compliance and transfer systems expert;
        * Major banking modules contributor.

Quentin Defenouillère <quentin.defenouillere@budget-insight.com>
        * Banking modules specialist (Credit Agricole, Groupama, Humanis);
        * Extensive banking modules work.

Vincent Ardisson <vardisson@budget-insight.com>
        * Performance optimization and modules maintenance expert;
        * Optimization and reliability improvements.

Florian Duguet <florian.duguet@budget-insight.com>
        * Documents and bills modules specialist;
        * Document handling systems.

Sylvie Ye <sylvie.ye@budget-insight.com>
        * Banking transfers and recipients API expert;
        * Transfer systems implementation.

Edouard Lambert <elambert@budget-insight.com>
        * S2E modules and various banking backends maintainer;
        * Banking modules diversification.

Guillaume Risbourg <guillaume.risbourg@budget-insight.com>
        * Multiple banking and bill modules contributor;
        * Diverse modules maintenance.

Maxime Gasselin <maxime.gasselin@budget-insight.com>
        * Banking modules contributor;
        * Banking systems support.

Damien Mat <damien.mat@budget-insight.com>
        * Various modules contributor;
        * Modules maintenance and improvements.

Jonathan Schmidt <jonathan.schmidt@budget-insight.com>
        * Banking and bill modules specialist;
        * Financial modules contributor.

Julien Louvel <julien.louvel@budget-insight.com>
        * Active banking and bill modules contributor (2021-2023);
        * Extensive modules maintenance and improvements.

Damien Ramelet <damien.ramelet@budget-insight.com>
        * Banking modules contributor (2021-2022);
        * Modules maintenance and bug fixes.

